Date: December 11th 2020

Summary: Cars clipping through floors

Priority or Severity: B

Visibility: High

Type: Vehicle

Reproduction Rate: 20%

Description: At random when driving, when the player or AI collides with another vehicle, there is a chance it will clip through the ground, rendering it unable to move

Load up the game
Click New or Continue Game
Find a vehicle of any kind
Crash into another vehicle

Results: Chance of clipping through the floor

Expected results: Collision physics applied
